title.rendered: STEDI SHORT TYPE PUSH SWITCH TO SUIT SUZUKI

content.rendered:
Short Type Push Switches to suit Suzuki JB74W Jimny

DETAILS

STEDI’s new range of Mitsubishi illuminated Push Button suit a number of modern Mitsubishi vehicles with OEM like fitment and finish.

KEY FEATURES

  • Ice Blue | Green Upper LED Back Lighting
  • Upper Light is Active when Power is ON
  • Lower Light is Active when Dash Lights are ON
  • Laser Etched print ensure our print will never rub off with use
  • Rated at 3A on 12v
  • Excellent OEM matching design

COMPATIBLE Mitsubishi MAKES

  • Mitsubishi Mirage | LA Series
  • Mitsubishi Outlander | ZK Series
  • Mitsubishi Pajero Sport | QE Series
  • Mitsubishi Triton | MQ Series & MR series

Please ensure our switches are always wired through a fused relay.

SPECIFICATIONS

BACK LIGHT COLOUR Blue
SURFACE SIZE DIMENSIONS 32.5mmx22mm
RATED 3A @ 12v

 

WHAT’S IN THE BOX

  • Short Type Push Button Switch
  • Wiring Diagram
